  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300°F (150°C).",
    "Season the beef brisket with caraway seeds, allspice, and salt.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, brown the beef on all sides over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion to the pot and cook until caramelized.",
    "Add the flour to the pot and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the stock to the pot, scraping up any browned bits from the bottom.",
    "Transfer the pot to the preheated oven and cook for 2 1/2 hours.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and let the beef rest for 10 minutes.",
    "Slice the beef against the grain and serve with the slaw mix, chopped parsley, and bonito flakes on top."
